---
title: Creamy Beef & Basil Pesto Penne with Leek
description: It’s pesto and beef in a creamy sauce. This already sounds like an amazing and tasty time but if you want to go the extra mile, add the leek and a zap of lemon to the pasta for flavour and smiles.

*Unfortunately, this
week's orecchiette was
in short supply, so we've
replaced it with penne.
Don't worry, the recipe
will be just as delicious,
just be sure to follow your
recipe card! *
